[
  {
    "startTime": 16.26,
    "endTime": 18.26,
    "text": "I woke up in the middle of the night"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.26,
    "endTime": 21.26,
    "text": "with the sound of heavy explosion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.26,
    "endTime": 23.26,
    "text": "It was deep at night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.26,
    "endTime": 25.26,
    "text": "I do not remember what time it was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.26,
    "endTime": 27.26,
    "text": "I just remember the sound"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.26,
    "endTime": 29.26,
    "text": "was so heavy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.26,
    "endTime": 32.260000000000005,
    "text": "and so very shocking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.26,
    "endTime": 35.26,
    "text": "Everything in my room was shaking --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.26,
    "endTime": 38.26,
    "text": "my heart, my windows,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.26,
    "endTime": 42.26,
    "text": "my bed, everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.26,
    "endTime": 45.26,
    "text": "I looked out the windows"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.26,
    "endTime": 48.26,
    "text": "and I saw a full half-circle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.26,
    "endTime": 50.26,
    "text": "of explosion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.26,
    "endTime": 52.26,
    "text": "I thought it was just like the movies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.26,
    "endTime": 54.26,
    "text": "but the movies had not conveyed them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.26,
    "endTime": 57.26,
    "text": "in the powerful image that I was seeing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.26,
    "endTime": 59.26,
    "text": "full of bright red"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.26,
    "endTime": 61.26,
    "text": "and orange and gray,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.26,
    "endTime": 63.26,
    "text": "and a full circle of explosion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.26,
    "endTime": 66.25999999999999,
    "text": "And I kept on staring at it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.26,
    "endTime": 69.26,
    "text": "until it disappeared."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.26,
    "endTime": 72.26,
    "text": "I went back to my bed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.26,
    "endTime": 74.26,
    "text": "and I prayed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.26,
    "endTime": 77.26,
    "text": "and I secretly thanked God"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.26,
    "endTime": 79.26,
    "text": "that that missile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.26,
    "endTime": 83.26,
    "text": "did not land on my family's home,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.26,
    "endTime": 88.26,
    "text": "that it did not kill my family that night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.26,
    "endTime": 90.26,
    "text": "Thirty years have passed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.26,
    "endTime": 94.26,
    "text": "and I still feel guilty about that prayer,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.26,
    "endTime": 96.26,
    "text": "for the next day, I learned that that missile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.26,
    "endTime": 100.26,
    "text": "landed on my brother's friend's home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.26,
    "endTime": 103.26,
    "text": "and killed him"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.26,
    "endTime": 105.26,
    "text": "and his father,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.26,
    "endTime": 111.26,
    "text": "but did not kill his mother or his sister."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.26,
    "endTime": 113.26,
    "text": "His mother showed up the next week"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.26,
    "endTime": 115.26,
    "text": "at my brother's classroom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.26,
    "endTime": 118.26,
    "text": "and begged seven-year-old kids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.26,
    "endTime": 121.26,
    "text": "to share with her any picture they may have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.26,
    "endTime": 123.26,
    "text": "of her son,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.26,
    "endTime": 129.26,
    "text": "for she had lost everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.26,
    "endTime": 131.26,
    "text": "This is not a story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.26,
    "endTime": 135.26,
    "text": "of a nameless survivor of war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.26,
    "endTime": 137.26,
    "text": "and nameless refugees,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.26,
    "endTime": 140.26,
    "text": "whose stereotypical images we see in our newspapers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.26,
    "endTime": 143.26,
    "text": "and our TV"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.26,
    "endTime": 145.26,
    "text": "with tattered clothes,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.26,
    "endTime": 149.26,
    "text": "dirty face, scared eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.26,
    "endTime": 152.26,
    "text": "This is not a story of a nameless someone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.26,
    "endTime": 154.26,
    "text": "who lived in some war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.26,
    "endTime": 156.26,
    "text": "who we do not know their hopes, their dreams,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.26,
    "endTime": 159.26,
    "text": "their accomplishments, their families,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.26,
    "endTime": 161.26,
    "text": "their beliefs, their values."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.26,
    "endTime": 165.26,
    "text": "This is my story."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.26,
    "endTime": 169.26,
    "text": "I was that girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.26,
    "endTime": 172.26,
    "text": "I am another image and vision"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.26,
    "endTime": 175.26,
    "text": "of another survivor of war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.26,
    "endTime": 177.26,
    "text": "I am that refugee,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.26,
    "endTime": 180.26,
    "text": "and I am that girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.26,
    "endTime": 182.26,
    "text": "You see,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.26,
    "endTime": 186.26,
    "text": "I grew up in war-torn Iraq,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.26,
    "endTime": 189.26,
    "text": "and I believe that there are two sides of wars"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.26,
    "endTime": 191.26,
    "text": "and we've only seen"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.26,
    "endTime": 193.26,
    "text": "one side of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.26,
    "endTime": 195.26,
    "text": "We only talk about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.26,
    "endTime": 197.26,
    "text": "one side of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.26,
    "endTime": 199.26,
    "text": "But there's another side"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.26,
    "endTime": 201.26,
    "text": "that I have witnessed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.26,
    "endTime": 203.26,
    "text": "as someone who lived in it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.26,
    "endTime": 206.26,
    "text": "and someone who ended up working in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.26,
    "endTime": 209.26,
    "text": "I grew up with the colors of war --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.26,
    "endTime": 212.26,
    "text": "the red colors of fire and blood,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.26,
    "endTime": 215.26,
    "text": "the brown tones of earth"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.26,
    "endTime": 217.26,
    "text": "as it explodes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.26,
    "endTime": 219.26,
    "text": "in our faces"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.26,
    "endTime": 221.26,
    "text": "and the piercing silver"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.26,
    "endTime": 223.26,
    "text": "of an exploded missile,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.26,
    "endTime": 225.26,
    "text": "so bright"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.26,
    "endTime": 229.26,
    "text": "that nothing can protect your eyes from it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.26,
    "endTime": 231.26,
    "text": "I grew up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.26,
    "endTime": 233.26,
    "text": "with the sounds of war --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.26,
    "endTime": 236.26,
    "text": "the staccato sounds of gunfire,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.26,
    "endTime": 239.26,
    "text": "the wrenching booms of explosions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.26,
    "endTime": 242.26,
    "text": "ominous drones of jets flying overhead"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.26,
    "endTime": 244.26,
    "text": "and the wailing warning sounds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.26,
    "endTime": 247.26,
    "text": "of sirens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.26,
    "endTime": 250.26,
    "text": "These are the sounds you would expect,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.26,
    "endTime": 252.26,
    "text": "but they are also the sounds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.26,
    "endTime": 255.26,
    "text": "of dissonant concerts of a flock of birds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.26,
    "endTime": 257.26,
    "text": "screeching in the night,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.26,
    "endTime": 259.26,
    "text": "the high-pitched honest cries"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.26,
    "endTime": 261.26,
    "text": "of children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.26,
    "endTime": 263.26,
    "text": "and the thunderous,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.26,
    "endTime": 265.26,
    "text": "unbearable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.26,
    "endTime": 268.26,
    "text": "silence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.26,
    "endTime": 270.26,
    "text": "\"War,\" a friend of mine said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.26,
    "endTime": 273.26,
    "text": "\"is not about sound at all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.26,
    "endTime": 276.26,
    "text": "It is actually about silence,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.26,
    "endTime": 281.26,
    "text": "the silence of humanity.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.26,
    "endTime": 284.26,
    "text": "I have since left Iraq"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.26,
    "endTime": 287.26,
    "text": "and founded a group called Women for Women International"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.26,
    "endTime": 289.26,
    "text": "that ends up working"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.26,
    "endTime": 292.26,
    "text": "with women survivors of wars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.26,
    "endTime": 294.26,
    "text": "In my travels and in my work,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.26,
    "endTime": 297.26,
    "text": "from Congo to Afghanistan,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.26,
    "endTime": 299.26,
    "text": "from Sudan to Rwanda,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.26,
    "endTime": 301.26,
    "text": "I have learned not only"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.26,
    "endTime": 304.26,
    "text": "that the colors and the sounds of war are the same,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.26,
    "endTime": 308.26,
    "text": "but the fears of war are the same."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.26,
    "endTime": 310.26,
    "text": "You know, there is a fear of dying,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.26,
    "endTime": 313.26,
    "text": "and do not believe any movie character"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.26,
    "endTime": 315.26,
    "text": "where the hero is not afraid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.26,
    "endTime": 317.26,
    "text": "It is very scary"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.26,
    "endTime": 319.26,
    "text": "to go through that feeling"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.26,
    "endTime": 321.26,
    "text": "of \"I am about to die\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.26,
    "endTime": 324.26,
    "text": "or \"I could die in this explosion.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.26,
    "endTime": 326.26,
    "text": "But there's also the fear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.26,
    "endTime": 328.26,
    "text": "of losing loved ones,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.26,
    "endTime": 330.26,
    "text": "and I think that's even worse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.26,
    "endTime": 333.26,
    "text": "It's too painful. You don't want to think about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.26,
    "endTime": 337.26,
    "text": "But I think the worst kind of fear is the fear --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.26,
    "endTime": 340.26,
    "text": "as Samia, a Bosnian woman, once told me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.26,
    "endTime": 343.26,
    "text": "who survived the four-years besiege of Sarajevo;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.26,
    "endTime": 345.26,
    "text": "she said, \"The fear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.26,
    "endTime": 347.26,
    "text": "of losing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.26,
    "endTime": 349.26,
    "text": "the 'I' in me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.26,
    "endTime": 352.26,
    "text": "the fear of losing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.26,
    "endTime": 354.26,
    "text": "the 'I' in me.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.26,
    "endTime": 356.26,
    "text": "That's what my mother in Iraq"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.26,
    "endTime": 358.26,
    "text": "used to tell me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.26,
    "endTime": 362.26,
    "text": "It's like dying from inside-out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.26,
    "endTime": 364.26,
    "text": "A Palestinian woman once told me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.26,
    "endTime": 367.26,
    "text": "\"It is not about the fear of one death,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.26,
    "endTime": 369.26,
    "text": "she said, \"sometimes I feel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.26,
    "endTime": 372.26,
    "text": "I die 10 times in one day,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.26,
    "endTime": 374.26,
    "text": "as she was describing the marches of soldiers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.26,
    "endTime": 376.26,
    "text": "and the sounds of their bullets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.26,
    "endTime": 378.26,
    "text": "She said, \"But it's not fair,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.26,
    "endTime": 381.26,
    "text": "because there is only one life,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.26,
    "endTime": 387.26,
    "text": "and there should only be one death.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.26,
    "endTime": 390.26,
    "text": "We have been only seeing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.26,
    "endTime": 392.26,
    "text": "one side of war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.26,
    "endTime": 395.26,
    "text": "We have only been discussing and consumed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.26,
    "endTime": 397.26,
    "text": "with high-level preoccupations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.26,
    "endTime": 400.26,
    "text": "over troop levels, drawdown timelines,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.26,
    "endTime": 402.26,
    "text": "surges and sting operations,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.26,
    "endTime": 405.26,
    "text": "when we should be examining the details"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.26,
    "endTime": 408.26,
    "text": "of where the social fabric"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.26,
    "endTime": 411.26,
    "text": "has been most torn,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.26,
    "endTime": 413.26,
    "text": "where the community has improvised"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.26,
    "endTime": 415.26,
    "text": "and survived"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.26,
    "endTime": 417.26,
    "text": "and shown acts of resilience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.26,
    "endTime": 419.26,
    "text": "and amazing courage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.26,
    "endTime": 423.26,
    "text": "just to keep life going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 423.26,
    "endTime": 426.26,
    "text": "We have been so consumed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.26,
    "endTime": 428.26,
    "text": "with seemingly objective discussions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.26,
    "endTime": 430.26,
    "text": "of politics, tactics,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.26,
    "endTime": 432.26,
    "text": "weapons, dollars"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432.26,
    "endTime": 434.26,
    "text": "and casualties."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.26,
    "endTime": 436.26,
    "text": "This is the language"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.26,
    "endTime": 439.26,
    "text": "of sterility."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.26,
    "endTime": 441.26,
    "text": "How casually"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.26,
    "endTime": 443.26,
    "text": "we treat casualties"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.26,
    "endTime": 445.26,
    "text": "in the context of this topic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.26,
    "endTime": 448.26,
    "text": "This is where we conceive of rape and casualties"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.26,
    "endTime": 451.26,
    "text": "as inevitabilities."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.26,
    "endTime": 454.26,
    "text": "Eighty percent of refugees around the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.26,
    "endTime": 457.26,
    "text": "are women and children. Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457.26,
    "endTime": 459.26,
    "text": "Ninety percent of modern war casualties"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.26,
    "endTime": 461.26,
    "text": "are civilians."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.26,
    "endTime": 464.26,
    "text": "Seventy-five percent of them are women and children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.26,
    "endTime": 467.26,
    "text": "How interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.26,
    "endTime": 469.26,
    "text": "Oh, half a million women in Rwanda"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.26,
    "endTime": 471.26,
    "text": "get raped in 100 days."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.26,
    "endTime": 474.26,
    "text": "Or, as we speak now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 474.26,
    "endTime": 477.26,
    "text": "hundreds of thousands of Congolese women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.26,
    "endTime": 479.26,
    "text": "are getting raped and mutilated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.26,
    "endTime": 481.26,
    "text": "How interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.26,
    "endTime": 485.26,
    "text": "These just become numbers that we refer to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.26,
    "endTime": 487.26,
    "text": "The front of wars"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 487.26,
    "endTime": 490.26,
    "text": "is increasingly non-human eyes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.26,
    "endTime": 492.26,
    "text": "peering down on our perceived enemies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.26,
    "endTime": 494.26,
    "text": "from space,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.26,
    "endTime": 497.26,
    "text": "guiding missiles toward unseen targets,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.26,
    "endTime": 499.26,
    "text": "while the human conduct"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.26,
    "endTime": 501.26,
    "text": "of the orchestra of media relations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.26,
    "endTime": 504.26,
    "text": "in the event that this particular drone attack"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 504.26,
    "endTime": 506.26,
    "text": "hits a villager"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 506.26,
    "endTime": 508.26,
    "text": "instead of an extremist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.26,
    "endTime": 510.26,
    "text": "It is a chess game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.26,
    "endTime": 513.26,
    "text": "You learn to play an international relations school"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.26,
    "endTime": 515.26,
    "text": "on your way out and up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.26,
    "endTime": 518.26,
    "text": "to national and international leadership."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.26,
    "endTime": 521.26,
    "text": "Checkmate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 521.26,
    "endTime": 523.26,
    "text": "We are missing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 523.26,
    "endTime": 527.26,
    "text": "a completely other side of wars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.26,
    "endTime": 530.26,
    "text": "We are missing my mother's story,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.26,
    "endTime": 533.26,
    "text": "who made sure with every siren, with every raid,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533.26,
    "endTime": 535.26,
    "text": "with every cut off-of electricity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.26,
    "endTime": 537.26,
    "text": "she played puppet shows for my brothers and I,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.26,
    "endTime": 539.26,
    "text": "so we would not be scared"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539.26,
    "endTime": 541.26,
    "text": "of the sounds of explosions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.26,
    "endTime": 544.26,
    "text": "We are missing the story of Fareeda,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.26,
    "endTime": 546.26,
    "text": "a music teacher,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 546.26,
    "endTime": 548.26,
    "text": "a piano teacher, in Sarajevo,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.26,
    "endTime": 550.26,
    "text": "who made sure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.26,
    "endTime": 552.26,
    "text": "that she kept the music school open"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.26,
    "endTime": 554.26,
    "text": "every single day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.26,
    "endTime": 557.26,
    "text": "in the four years of besiege in Sarajevo"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557.26,
    "endTime": 559.26,
    "text": "and walked to that school,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.26,
    "endTime": 561.26,
    "text": "despite the snipers shooting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.26,
    "endTime": 563.26,
    "text": "at that school and at her,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.26,
    "endTime": 566.26,
    "text": "and kept the piano, the violin, the cello"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.26,
    "endTime": 569.26,
    "text": "playing the whole duration of the war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.26,
    "endTime": 572.26,
    "text": "with students wearing their gloves and hats and coats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.26,
    "endTime": 574.26,
    "text": "That was her fight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 574.26,
    "endTime": 577.26,
    "text": "That was her resistance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 577.26,
    "endTime": 580.26,
    "text": "We are missing the story of Nehia,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.26,
    "endTime": 582.26,
    "text": "a Palestinian woman in Gaza"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.26,
    "endTime": 585.26,
    "text": "who, the minute there was a cease-fire in the last year's war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.26,
    "endTime": 587.26,
    "text": "she left out of home,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.26,
    "endTime": 589.26,
    "text": "collected all the flour"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.26,
    "endTime": 592.26,
    "text": "and baked as much bread for every neighbor to have,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.26,
    "endTime": 596.26,
    "text": "in case there is no cease-fire the day after."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 596.26,
    "endTime": 598.26,
    "text": "We are missing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 598.26,
    "endTime": 600.26,
    "text": "the stories of Violet,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.26,
    "endTime": 603.26,
    "text": "who, despite surviving genocide in the church massacre,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.26,
    "endTime": 605.26,
    "text": "she kept on going on,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 605.26,
    "endTime": 608.26,
    "text": "burying bodies, cleaning homes, cleaning the streets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.26,
    "endTime": 611.26,
    "text": "We are missing stories of women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 611.26,
    "endTime": 614.26,
    "text": "who are literally keeping life going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614.26,
    "endTime": 616.26,
    "text": "in the midst of wars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.26,
    "endTime": 618.26,
    "text": "Do you know --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.26,
    "endTime": 621.26,
    "text": "do you know that people fall in love in war"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.26,
    "endTime": 624.26,
    "text": "and go to school"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.26,
    "endTime": 626.26,
    "text": "and go to factories and hospitals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 626.26,
    "endTime": 628.26,
    "text": "and get divorced and go dancing and go playing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.26,
    "endTime": 632.26,
    "text": "and live life going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.26,
    "endTime": 634.26,
    "text": "And the ones who are keeping that life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.26,
    "endTime": 637.26,
    "text": "are women."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 637.26,
    "endTime": 641.26,
    "text": "There are two sides of war."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.26,
    "endTime": 643.26,
    "text": "There is a side that fights,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.26,
    "endTime": 645.26,
    "text": "and there is a side that keeps the schools"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.26,
    "endTime": 648.26,
    "text": "and the factories and the hospitals open."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.26,
    "endTime": 651.26,
    "text": "There is a side that is focused on winning battles,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.26,
    "endTime": 653.26,
    "text": "and there is a side that is focused"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653.26,
    "endTime": 656.26,
    "text": "on winning life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.26,
    "endTime": 659.26,
    "text": "There is a side that leads the front-line discussion,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659.26,
    "endTime": 661.26,
    "text": "and there is a side"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.26,
    "endTime": 664.26,
    "text": "that leads the back-line discussion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.26,
    "endTime": 666.26,
    "text": "There is a side that thinks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666.26,
    "endTime": 670.26,
    "text": "that peace is the end of fighting,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 670.26,
    "endTime": 672.26,
    "text": "and there is a side that thinks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 672.26,
    "endTime": 674.26,
    "text": "that peace is the arrival"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 674.26,
    "endTime": 677.26,
    "text": "of schools and jobs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 677.26,
    "endTime": 679.26,
    "text": "There is a side"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 679.26,
    "endTime": 681.26,
    "text": "that is led by men,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681.26,
    "endTime": 683.26,
    "text": "and there is a side"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.26,
    "endTime": 685.26,
    "text": "that is led by women."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.26,
    "endTime": 688.26,
    "text": "And in order for us to understand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688.26,
    "endTime": 691.26,
    "text": "how do we build lasting peace,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 691.26,
    "endTime": 694.26,
    "text": "we must understand war and peace"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 694.26,
    "endTime": 696.26,
    "text": "from both sides."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.26,
    "endTime": 698.26,
    "text": "We must have a full picture"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 698.26,
    "endTime": 700.26,
    "text": "of what that means."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 700.26,
    "endTime": 702.26,
    "text": "In order for us to understand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 702.26,
    "endTime": 704.26,
    "text": "what actually peace means,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 704.26,
    "endTime": 706.26,
    "text": "we need to understand,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 706.26,
    "endTime": 708.26,
    "text": "as one Sudanese woman once told me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 708.26,
    "endTime": 711.26,
    "text": "\"Peace is the fact that my toenails"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.26,
    "endTime": 714.26,
    "text": "are growing back again.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 714.26,
    "endTime": 716.26,
    "text": "She grew up in Sudan, in Southern Sudan,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.26,
    "endTime": 718.26,
    "text": "for 20 years of war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.26,
    "endTime": 721.26,
    "text": "where it killed one million people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.26,
    "endTime": 724.26,
    "text": "and displaced five million refugees."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.26,
    "endTime": 726.26,
    "text": "Many women were taken as slaves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 726.26,
    "endTime": 728.26,
    "text": "by rebels and soldiers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 728.26,
    "endTime": 731.26,
    "text": "as sexual slaves who were forced also"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 731.26,
    "endTime": 733.26,
    "text": "to carry the ammunition and the water"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 733.26,
    "endTime": 735.26,
    "text": "and the food for the soldiers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735.26,
    "endTime": 738.26,
    "text": "So that woman walked for 20 years,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 738.26,
    "endTime": 741.26,
    "text": "so she would not be kidnapped again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 741.26,
    "endTime": 744.26,
    "text": "And only when there was some sort of peace,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 744.26,
    "endTime": 748.26,
    "text": "her toenails grew back again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 748.26,
    "endTime": 750.26,
    "text": "We need to understand peace"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 750.26,
    "endTime": 754.26,
    "text": "from a toenail's perspective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 754.26,
    "endTime": 756.26,
    "text": "We need to understand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 756.26,
    "endTime": 758.26,
    "text": "that we cannot actually have negotiations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 758.26,
    "endTime": 760.26,
    "text": "of ending of wars or peace"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 760.26,
    "endTime": 763.26,
    "text": "without fully including women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 763.26,
    "endTime": 765.26,
    "text": "at the negotiating table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765.26,
    "endTime": 767.26,
    "text": "I find it amazing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 767.26,
    "endTime": 769.26,
    "text": "that the only group of people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 769.26,
    "endTime": 771.26,
    "text": "who are not fighting and not killing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 771.26,
    "endTime": 774.26,
    "text": "and not pillaging and not burning and not raping,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 774.26,
    "endTime": 776.26,
    "text": "and the group of people who are mostly --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 776.26,
    "endTime": 778.26,
    "text": "though not exclusively --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 778.26,
    "endTime": 781.26,
    "text": "who are keeping life going in the midst of war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 781.26,
    "endTime": 786.26,
    "text": "are not included in the negotiating table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 786.26,
    "endTime": 789.26,
    "text": "And I do argue that women lead the back-line discussion,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 789.26,
    "endTime": 791.26,
    "text": "but there are also men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 791.26,
    "endTime": 793.26,
    "text": "who are excluded from that discussion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 793.26,
    "endTime": 795.26,
    "text": "The doctors who are not fighting,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.26,
    "endTime": 798.26,
    "text": "the artists, the students, the men who refuse to pick up the guns,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 798.26,
    "endTime": 800.26,
    "text": "they are, too, excluded"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 800.26,
    "endTime": 803.26,
    "text": "from the negotiating tables."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 803.26,
    "endTime": 806.26,
    "text": "There is no way we can talk about a lasting peace,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 806.26,
    "endTime": 809.26,
    "text": "building of democracy, sustainable economies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 809.26,
    "endTime": 811.26,
    "text": "any kind of stabilities,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 811.26,
    "endTime": 814.26,
    "text": "if we do not fully include women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 814.26,
    "endTime": 816.26,
    "text": "at the negotiating table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 816.26,
    "endTime": 820.26,
    "text": "Not one, but 50 percent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 820.26,
    "endTime": 823.26,
    "text": "There is no way we can talk about the building of stability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 823.26,
    "endTime": 826.26,
    "text": "if we don't start investing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 826.26,
    "endTime": 828.26,
    "text": "in women and girls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 828.26,
    "endTime": 830.26,
    "text": "Did you know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 830.26,
    "endTime": 832.26,
    "text": "that one year"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 832.26,
    "endTime": 834.26,
    "text": "of the world's military spending"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 834.26,
    "endTime": 837.26,
    "text": "equals 700 years"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 837.26,
    "endTime": 840.26,
    "text": "of the U.N. budget"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 840.26,
    "endTime": 843.26,
    "text": "and equals 2,928 years"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 843.26,
    "endTime": 847.26,
    "text": "of the U.N. budget allocated for women?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 847.26,
    "endTime": 849.26,
    "text": "If we just reverse"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849.26,
    "endTime": 851.26,
    "text": "that distribution of funds,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 851.26,
    "endTime": 854.26,
    "text": "perhaps we could have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 854.26,
    "endTime": 857.26,
    "text": "a better lasting peace in this world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 857.26,
    "endTime": 859.26,
    "text": "And last, but not least,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 859.26,
    "endTime": 862.26,
    "text": "we need to invest in peace and women,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 862.26,
    "endTime": 865.26,
    "text": "not only because it is the right thing to do,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 865.26,
    "endTime": 868.26,
    "text": "not only because it is the right thing to do,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 868.26,
    "endTime": 871.26,
    "text": "for all of us to build sustainable and lasting peace today,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 871.26,
    "endTime": 874.26,
    "text": "but it is for the future."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 874.26,
    "endTime": 876.26,
    "text": "A Congolese woman,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 876.26,
    "endTime": 878.26,
    "text": "who was telling me about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 878.26,
    "endTime": 881.26,
    "text": "how her children saw their father killed in front of them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 881.26,
    "endTime": 884.26,
    "text": "and saw her raped in front of them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 884.26,
    "endTime": 886.26,
    "text": "and mutilated in front of them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 886.26,
    "endTime": 888.26,
    "text": "and her children saw their nine-year-old sibling"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 888.26,
    "endTime": 891.26,
    "text": "killed in front of them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 891.26,
    "endTime": 894.26,
    "text": "how they're doing okay right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 894.26,
    "endTime": 896.26,
    "text": "She got into Women for Women International's program."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 896.26,
    "endTime": 898.26,
    "text": "She got a support network."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 898.26,
    "endTime": 900.26,
    "text": "She learned about her rights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 900.26,
    "endTime": 903.26,
    "text": "We taught her vocational and business skills. We helped her get a job."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 903.26,
    "endTime": 906.26,
    "text": "She was earning 450 dollars. She was doing okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 906.26,
    "endTime": 908.26,
    "text": "She was sending them to school. Have a new home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 908.26,
    "endTime": 911.26,
    "text": "She said, \"But what I worry about the most"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 911.26,
    "endTime": 913.26,
    "text": "is not any of that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 913.26,
    "endTime": 915.26,
    "text": "I worry that my children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 915.26,
    "endTime": 918.26,
    "text": "have hate in their hearts,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 918.26,
    "endTime": 921.26,
    "text": "and when they want to grow up, they want to fight again"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 921.26,
    "endTime": 925.26,
    "text": "the killers of their father and their brother.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 925.26,
    "endTime": 928.26,
    "text": "We need to invest in women,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 928.26,
    "endTime": 931.26,
    "text": "because that's our only chance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 931.26,
    "endTime": 933.26,
    "text": "to ensure that there is no more war"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 933.26,
    "endTime": 935.26,
    "text": "in the future."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 935.26,
    "endTime": 938.26,
    "text": "That mother has a better chance to heal her children"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 938.26,
    "endTime": 942.26,
    "text": "than any peace agreement can do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 942.26,
    "endTime": 945.26,
    "text": "Are there good news? Of course, there are good news. There are lots of good news."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 945.26,
    "endTime": 948.26,
    "text": "To start with, these women that I told you about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 948.26,
    "endTime": 951.26,
    "text": "are dancing and singing every single day,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 951.26,
    "endTime": 953.26,
    "text": "and if they can,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 953.26,
    "endTime": 955.26,
    "text": "who are we not to dance?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 955.26,
    "endTime": 957.26,
    "text": "That girl that I told you about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 957.26,
    "endTime": 960.26,
    "text": "ended up starting Women for Women International Group"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 960.26,
    "endTime": 963.26,
    "text": "that impacted one million people, sent 80 million dollars,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 963.26,
    "endTime": 965.26,
    "text": "and I started this from zero,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 965.26,
    "endTime": 968.26,
    "text": "nothing, nada, [unclear]."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 968.26,
    "endTime": 971.26,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 971.26,
    "endTime": 974.26,
    "text": "They are women who are standing on their feet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 974.26,
    "endTime": 977.26,
    "text": "in spite of their circumstances,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 977.26,
    "endTime": 980.26,
    "text": "not because of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 980.26,
    "endTime": 983.26,
    "text": "Think of how the world can be a much better place"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 983.26,
    "endTime": 985.26,
    "text": "if, for a change,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 985.26,
    "endTime": 987.26,
    "text": "we have a better equality,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 987.26,
    "endTime": 989.26,
    "text": "we have equality,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 989.26,
    "endTime": 991.26,
    "text": "we have a representation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 991.26,
    "endTime": 993.26,
    "text": "and we understand war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 993.26,
    "endTime": 995.26,
    "text": "both from the front-line"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 995.26,
    "endTime": 997.26,
    "text": "and the back-line discussion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 997.26,
    "endTime": 1000.26,
    "text": "Rumi, a 13th-century Sufi poet,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1000.26,
    "endTime": 1002.26,
    "text": "says, \"Out beyond the worlds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1002.26,
    "endTime": 1005.26,
    "text": "of right-doings and wrong-doings,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1005.26,
    "endTime": 1007.26,
    "text": "there is a field."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1007.26,
    "endTime": 1009.26,
    "text": "I will meet you there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1009.26,
    "endTime": 1012.26,
    "text": "When the soul lies down in that grass,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1012.26,
    "endTime": 1014.26,
    "text": "the world is too full"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1014.26,
    "endTime": 1016.26,
    "text": "to talk about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1016.26,
    "endTime": 1018.26,
    "text": "Ideas, language,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1018.26,
    "endTime": 1020.26,
    "text": "even the phrase 'each other'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1020.26,
    "endTime": 1024.26,
    "text": "no longer makes any sense.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1024.26,
    "endTime": 1027.26,
    "text": "I humbly add -- humbly add --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1027.26,
    "endTime": 1029.26,
    "text": "that out beyond"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1029.26,
    "endTime": 1032.26,
    "text": "the worlds of war and peace,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1032.26,
    "endTime": 1034.26,
    "text": "there is a field,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1034.26,
    "endTime": 1037.26,
    "text": "and there are many women and men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1037.26,
    "endTime": 1040.26,
    "text": "[who] are meeting there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1040.26,
    "endTime": 1043.26,
    "text": "Let us make this field a much bigger place."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1043.26,
    "endTime": 1046.26,
    "text": "Let us all meet in that field."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1046.26,
    "endTime": 1048.26,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1048.26,
    "endTime": 1058.26,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]